00:39:14.100 --> 00:39:18.140
It was, for many years, one of
the best venues in all of Florida,

00:39:18.140 --> 00:39:21.440
in terms of its acoustics
for music and theater.

00:39:21.440 --> 00:39:25.020 position:56%
And this is a celebration, or the --

00:39:25.020 --> 00:39:29.190
it's a meeting commemorating the
