00:45:48.050 --> 00:45:52.950 position:56%
All those years, she was
maintaining her Spanish citizenship.

00:45:52.950 --> 00:45:57.310 position:56%
And, only in '39, '40, '41, does she
go and become an American citizen.

00:45:57.310 --> 00:45:59.410
I think, maybe, she was
hoping that maybe she would,

00:45:59.410 --> 00:46:01.520
someday, go back to Spain.

00:46:01.520 --> 00:46:06.510
This is a beautiful Thanksgiving
dinner in San Leandro, California.

